<plot>A series of mysterious murders confounds the country's secret services, as they investigate, discreetly but persistently, every aspect of the case. With the help of a number of coincidences, it is revealed that the crimes are connected to the activity of foreign agents who operate in Greece. In the end, all these agents - although their origin is not specified - try to obtain valuable, ultra-top-secret documents that are related to certain "serious" experiments that are being secretly performed on a NATO military base.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?027832</url></doc>
